</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">qdelmin: range from -300 up to and including +300 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">qdelmax: range from -300 up to and including +300 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p ">When all parameters are in range the carriage speed is correct. 
